What international newspapers is in the Asia District?

answers.text: OK VIETIMES and Oklahoma Chinese Times

qas.question: What is the name of the student newspaper?

context: There are numerous community and international newspapers locally that cater to the city's ethnic mosaic; such as The Black Chronicle, headquartered in the <a0_0>Eastside<a0_0/>, the <a1_0>OK VIETIMES and Oklahoma Chinese Times<a1_0/>, located in Asia District, and various Hispanic community publications. <a2_0>The Campus<a2_0/> is the student newspaper at Oklahoma City University. Gay publications include The Gayly Oklahoman.
